{"tid":1471880,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個反送中運動入面你覺得有用既網站","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T02:13:39.000Z","uid":259787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb6a67235cab74c08c3c3e3beedebbf40c60659","tid":1471880,"uid":259787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:40:37.000Z","msg":"睇完下面link個篇文，佢建議： <br />\n群眾一方可以進步既地方就係做好自身既情報工作。根據我既觀察，群眾一方既資訊凌亂而分散，簡單而言，係連自己有幾多資源，點樣分配都唔知道。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">群眾一方可以考慮將資訊集中，令同行人更清楚局勢。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(連載長文 代post) 哈佛社會學博士生給連登仔的信<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aejNzLU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aejNzLU</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家一人N條link，講下今次反送中運動入面你覺得有用既網站</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我先：<br />\n<br />\n反送中直播台（可同時睇多台直播畫面）：<a href=\"https://ncehk2019.github.io/nce-live/?visibleCount=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fncehk2019.github.io%2Fnce-live%2F%3FvisibleCount%3D4&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3XHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=1b1995e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://ncehk2019.github.io/nce-live/?visibleCount=4</a><br />\n實時地圖：<a href=\"https://103.hk/map/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F103.hk%2Fmap%2F&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3XHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=12beb8f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://103.hk/map/</a><br />\n香城Online（裝備資訊，手機版+官方wiki）：<a href=\"https://beta.hackfoldr.org/hongkongonline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeta.hackfoldr.org%2Fhongkongonline&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3XHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=2671caf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://beta.hackfoldr.org/hongkongonline</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，整合左大家既link之後，建議以上各大網站都可以加哂呢堆link"},{"pid":"0c01475d719ec14c8c6e6e763848c7f1b1ab85d8","tid":1471880,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href